{
  "name": "Ring of Fire Elemental Command",
  "type": "equipment",
  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<div class=\"ddb\">\n<p>This ring is linked to the &amp;Reference[elemental]{Elemental} Plane of &amp;Reference[fire]{Fire}.</p>\n<p>While wearing this ring, you have advantage on attack rolls against &amp;Reference[fire]{fire} elementals, and they have disadvantage on attack rolls against you. In addition, you have access to properties based on the &amp;Reference[elemental]{Elemental} Plane of &amp;Reference[fire]{Fire}.</p>\n<p>The ring has 5 charges. It regains 1d4 + 1 expended charges daily at dawn. Spells cast from the ring have a save DC of 17.</p>\n<p>You can expend 2 of the ring's charges to cast <strong></strong><strong>dominate monster</strong> on a &amp;Reference[fire]{fire} &amp;Reference[elemental]{elemental}. In addition, you have resistance to &amp;Reference[fire]{fire} damage. You can also speak and understand Ignan.</p>\n<p>If you help slay a &amp;Reference[fire]{fire} &amp;Reference[elemental]{elemental} while attuned to the ring, you gain access to the following additional properties:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>You are immune to &amp;Reference[fire]{fire} damage.</li>\n<li>You can cast the following spells from the ring, expending the necessary number of charges: <strong></strong>@UUID[Compendium.world.ddb-lost-mines-phandelver-spells.Item.lAfkUIqhch8HUoLA]{burning hands} (1 charge), <strong></strong>@UUID[Compendium.world.ddb-lost-mines-phandelver-spells.Item.MAuGUEKDXVcV8JM6]{fireball} (2 charges), and <strong></strong>@UUID[Compendium.world.ddb-lost-mines-phandelver-spells.Item.H9YxSqtXKnbZBFMt]{wall of fire} (3 charges).<br /><br /></li>\n</ul>\n</div>",
